title: Chocolate, Coconut and Walnut Cookies
ingredients: ['225g butter, softened', '85g cream cheese', '110g dark brown soft sugar', '100g caster sugar', '2 eggs', '280g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '285g milk chocolate, chopped', '75g desiccated coconut', '200g chopped walnuts']
